# Git and IDE
**/.git
**/.idea
**/.vscode

# Node & Python
**/node_modules
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc

# Java build artifacts
**/target
!ojp/ojp-server/target/ojp-server-*.jar
**/*.class
**/build
**/.gradle

# Logs and temp
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/logs

# Large Archives
**/*.7z
**/*.zip
**/*.tar.gz
**/*.iso

